        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "BERT-base is usually the right starting point: it fits on a single GPU with a batch size of 32 and reaches within ~1 % of BERT-large on most tasks after fine-tuning. Use BERT-large when the dataset is small and you need maximum accuracy from frozen features."
